{
  "stem": "19518.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 255.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Those are the little things that made life quite interesting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And slowly the noose was getting tighter around our necks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You had to give up radio.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "You had to-- you had no-- you were not allowed to have a telephone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You were not allowed to have a radio.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You were not allowed to have a fur coat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You were not allowed to have a fur collar.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You were not allowed to have [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] certain necessities, actually.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had to bring voluntary to an-- an area that they recommend, that they specified, were to deposit.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then came the time where you, if you had a bank account, it wasn't yours anymore.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you had a few zlotys you had to give it up, and they exchange it for pittance and the deutsche marks.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Let's say if you went with 500 zlotys to exchange, you got the worst of 50 zlotys in the deutsche marks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They gave you 500, but that was nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, just the Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just the Jew, not the Poles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, the Poles were treated yet in a different manner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whoever had a nice apartment, and I'm speaking of luxury apartments, they had to not to give up completely.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they had to go into one room, the whole family, and to give the rest of the apartment for a German [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] officer.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If you had a maid, you had to let her go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you had to be-- become the maid for that officer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For this, he allowed you to stay in-- in that one room for the whole family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was the normal routine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was the norm.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We accepted that.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
